                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Delightful & Intelligent for Adults who love Harry & Kids</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
